<div class=Section1 style='layout-grid:15.6pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>梅州红中宝</span><span style='color:white'> </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>游戏规则</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>一、规则介绍</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>牌：一万到九万</span><span lang=EN-US
style='color:white'>,</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>一筒到九筒，一条到九条，各</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>张。东南西北中发白板各</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>张，合计：</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>136</span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>张牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>宝牌：红中宝麻将中，红中允许变做任意一张牌</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>,</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>可以跟其他牌凑着胡牌，但不能跟其他牌凑着碰或者杠。红中设置不能打出。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>游戏人数：</span><span lang=EN-US
style='color:white'>4</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>人。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>庄：游戏中采用连庄方式，仅第一局为系统随机定庄，之后将由本局胡牌的玩家下局坐庄，如庄家胡牌，则继续连庄。如出现和牌，则对方坐庄。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>5</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>马牌：</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:
white'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>马牌不参与摸牌，需要留牌。最后自摸者进行奖码（</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1,5,9</span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>，红中和东风，则中码）。如没红中自摸加奖多一个码。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>不用看庄家是谁，和风位。任何一个方位的玩家，都是以：</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1,5,9</span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>，红中，东风，则中奖。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>6</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>抓牌：庄家掷</span><span lang=EN-US
style='color:white'>2</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>个骰子，点子大的骰点是确认在谁面前的牌来抓（从庄家数起，单数为庄家面前的牌抓起，双数为对家牌面抓起），点子小的骰点是确定在第几墩来抓牌！由庄家开始拿牌，每次拿</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2</span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>墩。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>7</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>出牌：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>游戏在一开始，只有庄家可得到十四张牌，对方十三张。庄家从牌中选出一张最无用的牌丢出，此时，对方有权力要那张丢出的牌，</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>打牌过程中可碰、杠、补张、不能吃牌，吃胡，只能自己胡牌（除了地胡，可以吃胡）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>抢杠：</span><span style='color:white'> </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>玩家抢杠时将不能抢自己所打的牌，如：自己打出一张三条，有人杠，此时将无法对其进行抢杠操作。</span><span
lang=EN-US style='color:white'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>杠分明杠、放杠和暗杠。明杠是指手上有三张已碰出的牌，再摸上一张杠，叫明杠。放杠是指手上有三张相同牌，其它家打出这只牌时杠，叫放杠，暗杠是指手上摸到四张相同牌时杠，叫暗杠。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>杠牌者抓牌从牌尾抓起。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>8</span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>、</span><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>胡牌</span></p>

